OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIsrael condemns Lula       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flikening Gaza war to       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FHolocaust                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Israel has condemned Brazil's president
OL,6, after he accused Israel of committing  
OL,7, genocide in Gaza, comparing its actions
OL,8, to the Holocaust.                      
OL,10,FLuiz Inacio Lula da Silva said Israel's
OL,11,Fmilitary campaign was between a "highly
OL,12,Fprepared army and women and children". 
OL,14,FIsrael's foreign minister described    
OL,15,FLula's comments as antisemitic and said
OL,16,Fhe was "persona non grata" in the      
OL,17,Fcountry until he retracted them.       
OL,19,FThe main Jewish organisation in Brazil 
OL,20,Fhas also criticised Lula's comments.   
